# VulkanRender v4 procedural many-light deferred demo marker.
#
# The renderer recognizes this extension and builds a procedural scene with:
# - a 16x16 PBR sphere grid
# - visible colored light markers
# - a simple room/floor receiver for SSAO and local light falloff
#
# The actual many-light positions are generated procedurally in the v4 deferred
# composition shader so this marker stays small and easy to version.
